Notice Serial Number:  PN/SL/EM/09032022/01   312340091
You have failed to ensure that the electrical equipment , including the coiled extension lead, is suitably rated for adverse environments including wet environments

IN/SL/EM/09032022/01 - 312373769
You have failed to either prevent or, where this is not reasonably practicable, adequately control exposure of employees and members of the public to chemicals labelled as corrosive and/or harmful, which are substances hazardous to health in use at your car wash, because you are storing these chemicals in an area where food is prepared and outside in open containers where members of the public can access them.
